{"tid":377929,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗惇裕學校現「影子學生」　長期缺課獲升班　","createTime":"2017-08-28T05:47:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T08:42:52.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a15c9d12a001b574cd7f5261697a4f54d5846d12","tid":377929,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T05:47:27.000Z","msg":"繼屯門興德學校被揭有「影子學生」後，本報發現位於元朗新田的惇裕學校同樣出現「影子學生」。<br />\n本報獲得該校共5張成績表，至少涉及3個學生，在長時間缺席及沒有考試的情況下仍獲升班。校方回覆時承認事件，解釋該數名學生突然失去聯絡，基於人情保留其學位，並已通報教育局。<br />\n教育局則指校方的呈報及跟進程序須改善，亦不應為沒有合理原因而長期缺席的學生保留學位。<br />\n至於校方其後如何處理長期缺課情況？詳情請留意今天《明報》報道。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170828/s00001/1503848134540\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170828%2Fs00001%2F1503848134540&d=cc5Vyip4F%2BDnLp4ljgfpG5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=3e87abe0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170828%2Fs00001%2F1503848134540&h=9a9c3a12\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170828/s00001/1503848134540</a>"},{"pid":"dc503eec173791bedcf131bfaba9dc526df3640e","tid":377929,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T05:48:42.000Z","msg":"freemasonry?"},{"pid":"9575503b6cbda5a41912514797e390ffb7d0dbba","tid":377929,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T07:58:52.000Z","msg":"學生突然失去聯絡，唔係去報警 ?"},{"pid":"076d50ece05310f64b166e2fe2f3b749abd93f13","tid":377929,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T08:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}